description: A melting pot of music to listen to at work!  Over 40 hours of music! Pop, light rock, feel good, country, rock, alternative, classics, 80s, 90s...  Most songs are clean and safe for work (office). There are some odd ones added in by request of my coworkers but generally a good mix. Shuffle!
